  "texts": [
    "These results are similar to those reported by Kherwa and Bansal (2019) that the use of TM for image processing and detecting themes in video data sets is still underexplored.",
    "Based on the research trend, our result identifies the future research direction as Topic 3 (Medical record analysis), Topic 6 (Public health & social media), Topic 8 (Information mining), and Topic 9 (Literature review synthesis).",
    "Based on the discussion of the results above, this paper developed a conceptual framework (as illustrated in Fig. 8) to provide a summary of the TM application.",
    "The proposed conceptual framework reflects the current knowledge of TM applications which comprises a variety of key elements.",
    "For example, as shown in Fig. 8, there are domains in which TM has been applied ranging from the technology, communication, entertainment, security, humanities, legal, environmental, transportation, finance to medicine and healthcare domain."
  ]
}